                        Since its launch, this homepage has been called "kz's page". "Kz" is a combination of two letters from my first name, "lazuo". There is no deep meaning to it, I just remembered that someone I met while traveling called me "keizi", so I named it this.
                        I recently learned that "kz" is a character string that should not be used in German-speaking countries. Ignorance is a scary thing.
                        So I changed the name to "Contrail".
                        At present, the homepage service I am subscribed to does not support URL changes, so the URL will remain "kz-page", but
                        I would like to change the URL to "Contrail" if I have the opportunity.
                        このホームページは開設以来「kzのページ」と呼んでいます。「kz」は私の名前「lazuo」の2文字を組み合わせたものです。深い意味はなく、旅先で出会った人が「keizi」と呼んでいたのを思い出してこの名前にしました。
